y vide Penal Order  No. SEC/Enforcement/1086/2013/417, dated October 17, 2016.  ** BSEC vide letter No. BSEC/Mukhopattro (2nd Part)/2011/470, dated August 02, 2016 panalized Tk. 10 lacs.  DSE has approved the additional space of head office on October 18, 2017  # DSE has approved the closing of office space on September 28, 2021', 'Rahman Mansion (3rd Floor, West Side), 161, Motijheel C/A, Dhaka-1000', '47112064, 9512431, 9556146, 9560134', '8117784', NULL, '# Three traded IDs were added on 25/08/1998  # Three trader IDs were added on 25/08/1998  # One trader ID was added on 15/09/1998.  #  Shifted from WAN( Jareen Mansion , 3rd Flr., 55 MCA, Dhaka-1000) to LAN ( Room #        419F)on 26/10/2003 03/10/2004 : Suspended by SEC on 03/10/2004. 31/10/2004 : Resumed on 27/10/2004. 09/06/2005 : #Suspended by SEC on 09/06/2005 03/08/2005 : # Resumed on 12/06/2005 27/01/2009 : ', NULL, '500000000', '0', '224124861', '0', 'Mr. Reza - Ur- Rahman Sinha', 'CEO', '01/01/1900');

